data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath Two Story Colonial on Large Corner Lot with WONDERFUL INGROUND POOL. Large Living room and Dining Room with gleaming Hardwood Floors. First Floor Family room off the Kitchen w/ FIREPLACE. EAT-IN Kitchen with Newer SS Appliances.  The 2nd floor features 4 spacious bedrooms and 1 Full Baths.  The Lower Level is perfect for the kids as a recreation room. Outside there is a 18' x 36' In Ground Pool with a New Pump and Filter and Fire Pit. New Roof in 2020, New Water Softener, and Hot Water Heater. Move in Condition.  CHEERS TO YOUR NEW HOUSE IN THE NEW YEAR!!
